TASK_DESCRIPTION=Workers have a problem submitting messages after entering text. The send-keys mechanism enters the message content but fails to actually submit it (Enter key not registering, or submission blocked). This is a reliability issue in the send-keys dispatch pipeline. Investigate: 1) Is the Enter key being sent? 2) Is there a timing issue between text entry and Enter? 3) Is Claude Code blocking the submission? 4) Does the worker need an Escape first to exit any mode?
